response

Class ResponseStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • response.ResponseStatement

  • public class ResponseStatement
extends java.lang.Object
    ResponseStatement is a class which is used as an response template, containing the status of the operation, the errorMessage and the data. This class is used to be a standard type of response between processes
